content:
I just completed texting training last night. When and where will I get notified that I am approved?
Also why is the New Mod Recruitment channel Read-only for me? I see others are responding. I was a texting Mod here during Joe Biden’s run.

HI <@1277413673438023752> thank you so much for completing texting training! We really appreciate your volunteer efforts. It takes the team a little while to onboard everyone from the training sessions, and you will get a DM when they are ready for you. If you are still waiting on Monday you can send a reminder here https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1266829704204386334
<@1277413673438023752> the New Mod Recruitment channel is closed right now because staff is training volunteers who applied earlier. When we need more mods, the channel will re-open
Is it ok that I got one quiz question wrong? It was the first question I think. I sort of lost control of my finger and it twitched on the wrong answer (it does that when I’m tired!!)
You should ask about that in https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1266829704204386334
